dct_title_s: A new map of France, agreeable to its division into provinces, As previous to the Revolution
dct_description_sm: From the latest authorities ; By John Cary. Engraver. ; Printed for J. Cary Engraver & Map seller No. 86 St. James's Str. April 1st. 1824.
Three bar scales in "British Statute Miles," "Common French Leagues," "German Miles."
Shows cities and towns, land routes, waterways, province names.
